Package org.team1c.avs

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AvsCustomPartitioner
    Partitioner class to partition video inputs based on their ids
    AvsPublishCallback
    This function is to provide a completion message through asynchronous sending of Kafka producers
    HdfsWriter
    Hdfs writer which will be used to copy a file and store it into HDFS
    MongoWriter
    MongoDB writer class is used to insert data into MongoDB.
    Util
    Collection of miscellaneous utility functions that is used frequently.
    VideoEventGenerator
    This class is to generate events and push frames into Kafka broker by reading frames of input
    VideoStreamArchiver
    This class is used to create a VideoStreamWriter for each video input
    VideoStreamCollector
    This video takes in a property file and starts a VideoEventGenerator for each video input specified
    VideoStreamDashboard
    This class runs the dashboard of the system.
    VideoStreamProcessor
    This class performs real time video processing on image frames received from Kafka
    VideoStreamWriter
    This class is to write video frames and its data detected to MongoDB and HDFS
